on Education and Cultural Affairs pursuant to Joint Rule 308.2 and ordered printed.
DAREK M. GRANT
Secretary of the Senate
Presented by Senator GROHOSKI of Hancock.
Cosponsored by Representative BABIN of Fort Fairfield and
Senators: LIBBY of Cumberland, RAFFERTY of York, Representatives: CARLOW of
Buxton, DODGE of Belfast, FROST of Belgrade, GERE of Kennebunkport, MURPHY of
Scarborough, SARGENT of York.
Printed on recycled paper

